data.title: Port Code List Compress
data.meta_description: Port Code List Compress - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains a list of port codes and corresponding country codes and port names. There are over 500 entries listing ports from countries around the world in alphabetical order beginning with AD for Andorra and ending with AR for Argentina. Each entry includes the port code, country code, and full port name.
